  [ Mike Gabriel ]
  * Remove duplicate install of nxproxy from main Makefile. Spotted by Jan
    Engelhard.
  * Work-in patch from Jan Engehardt for working around different
    improper bash implementations of string-in-string replacing. (Fixes:
    #145).
